data.description: This Marion 2-story home with 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, central air, gas heat, and a 2-car detached garage is priced for quick sale! The property is currently rented by a long-term tenant for $800 a month who is willing to stay or move. The range and refrigerator stay. The electric hot water heater is approx 1 year old. 200 Amp electric panel. A new sump pump was installed approx 2022. Selling as is. Schedule your showing before this is gone!
